wpPost.title: FLS Supply Chain Center (FSCC) is fully completed!

seo.title: FLS Supply Chain Center (FSCC) is fully completed! - FLS
seo.metaDesc: Our FLS Supply Chain Center (FSCC) in Rayong, Thailand is now fully completed. Strategically located in Map Ta Phut Industrial Estate, our warehouse meets world-class requirements and is perfectly positioned to level up your supply chain.
seo.opengraphTitle: FLS Supply Chain Center (FSCC) is fully completed! - FLS
seo.opengraphDescription: Our FLS Supply Chain Center (FSCC) in Rayong, Thailand is now fully completed. Strategically located in Map Ta Phut Industrial Estate, our warehouse meets world-class requirements and is perfectly positioned to level up your supply chain.

blocks.name: core/paragraph
blocks.saveContent: All 11,000 sqm of facilities in the first FLS-owned warehouse went into operation, serving global clients in Map Ta Phut and Ban Khai Industrial Estates. FSCC is part of our bigger plan to accelerate the growth and become a significant player in the warehousing landscape.

blocks.name: core/paragraph
blocks.saveContent: In this fully-equipped warehouse, dangerous and non-dangerous cargo is stored, packed and repacked under international standards and ready for onward journeys around the world.

blocks.name: core/paragraph
blocks.saveContent: Our highly-experienced staff have had emergency response training, in cooperation with the local fire brigade, to meet all international safety standards.

blocks.name: core/paragraph
blocks.saveContent: After completing the Factory Acceptance Test in October 2022, our bespoke Industrial Repacking System has been installed in the specially sealed-off section at the FSCC. Since then, the new system has produced the first shipments for our clients in Japan and Korea.

blocks.name: core/paragraph
blocks.saveContent: As we currently have high demand at the FSCC, email us now to pre-book your space: warehousing@fls-group.com.
